            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Dominicus">Domenico</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName> e la
                        moglie <persName><name ref="Bona">Bonia</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Bonius">Bonio</name></persName>, con il consenso del
                        marito, interrogata dal <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">giudice del
                            sacro palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name
                                ref="Sigefredus">Sighifridi</name></persName>, vendono a
                                <persName><name ref="Rusticus">Rustico</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Stantius">Stanzio</name></persName>, un
                        appezzamento di terra, quod est campo, posto in loco et finibus ubi dicitur
                        al <placeName ref="#places/3107">Moio prope Spinatico</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> ambas capitas in vie
                        publiche, lato uno con terra loro, alio lato con terra delle figlie del
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">fu <name ref="Eriteus"
                                >Erizio</name></persName>, per una misura complessiva di 11 staia
                        con tutte le sue dipendenze, ricevendo da <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Pietro</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Morus"
                                >Moro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">meritum argentum</rs> pro 60 soldi. Chiedono
                        al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildebrando</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum in loco et
                        finibus Spinatico. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori:
                        Sighifridi iudex sacri palatii, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedetto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Paganus">Pagano</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Eriteus">Erizio</name></persName>. <rs
                            key="#Copyist">Copiatore</rs>: <persName key="#Copyist #Notary"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Copyist #Notary">notarius dom. imp.</rs>
                        <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
